        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">The European production volume of pure hydrogen in 2021 is 8.27 Mt, over 90% are produced by steam methane refoming.
Hydrogen, which is used directly in ammonia production, is integrated in the datasets 'ammonia production, steam reforming, liquid, RER and RU' and therefore it's production volume (6.45E+09 kg) is subtracted.

References:
Hydrogen Europe (2022): Clean hydrogen monitor 2022, available here: https://hydrogeneurope.eu/clean-hydrogen-monitor-2022/.
Hydrogen Europe (2021): Clean hydrogen monitor 2021, available here: https://hydrogeneurope.eu/product/clean-hydrogen-monitor-report-2021/</productionVolumeComment>
